Yesterday we caught up as he brought his wife down for a vacation.

A little after 4am last night @atxmeghan woke me up because Oso was in distress and his breathing was labored. I took him downstairs and held him while trying to get him calm and stable. While we were preparing to take him to the emergency vet, he passed on in my arms. We're not entirely certain what happened at this point but he's gone. He had a rough start before ending up at @texasferretloversrescue and then finding his forever home with us but he was handsome and smart and we loved him even when he expressed his love with his teeth. 

Go hug your pets.

#osoisyourbroso

An overdue 'Thank You!' to everyone who came out to the show last Friday at @delilahsfrontporch & of course, to Delilah's for having us and @vancertsatx for putting it all together. @peeyellow is a force of nature that simply cannot be denied and @atticted & @theghostwolves are what I've always loved about live music in Austin.

Also, have to mention @joelkeithjoel & @theamazingfacedanblock for their contributions to a really good time. Dan even (unofficially) broke his world record!
